    Navigating NovoEd & Slack

    Welcome to NovoEd, our online platform for Stanford Ignite. This site will serve to provide you with access to learning materials and program logistics. To get the most out of your experience, please review how all of our systems work below.

    Navigating NovoEd

    During the program, we will use NovoEd as a communications platform, a hub for releasing and collecting assignments, and a repository for program information, schedules, cases, and preparation materials. Read the following guide to familiarize yourself with NovoEd.

    NovoEd Guide.pdf
    Download File

    Navigating Slack

    During the program, we will use slack to connect participants before, during, and after the program. Read the following guide to familiarize yourself with Slack.

    Slack Guide.pdf
    Download File

    If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to program staff at gsb_ignite_full_time@stanford.edu.
